<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reservation Confirmation</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: white;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            background-color: rgb(212, 175, 55);
            color: rgb(34, 34, 34);
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .header h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: rgb(253, 246, 227);
        }

        .content h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .content ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 10px 0 20px;
        }

        .content ul li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: rgb(212, 175, 55);
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: rgb(212, 175, 55);
            color: rgb(34, 34, 34);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: rgb(175, 146, 46);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #555555;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }

        .footer img {
            max-width: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Reservation Confirmed!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Hello, <span>{{user}}</span>!</h1>
            <h2>Your reservation has been successfully confirmed!</h2>
            <p>Here are the details of your reservation:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Check-In Date:</strong> {{checkIn}}</li>
                <li><strong>Check-Out Date:</strong> {{checkOut}}</li>
                <li><strong>Total Amount:</strong> ${{totalAmount}}</li>
                <li><strong>Room:</strong> {{room}}</li>
                <li><strong>Cats Included:</strong> {{cats}}</li>
                <li><strong>Payment Status:</strong> {{payment}}</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We hope you enjoy your stay. Please feel free to contact us for any questions or additional requests.</p>
            <p style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;">Sincerely,<br>The Reservations Team</p>
            <a href="." class="button">Visit Our Website</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <img src="cid:logoApp" alt="Logo">
            <p>&copy; 2025 The Fancy Box. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>